frc-docs, the official FIRST documentation for FIRST Robotics Competition, is accepting new translators for the upcoming changes to the Control System Documentation especially targeting the rather large volume of changes set for 2027. Interested applicants can apply here and see the full process and details here

The current progress could not have been possible without our amazing language maintainers, reviewers and translators! Thank you, thank you, thank you.

Individuals wishing to contribute docs content: GitHub - wpilibsuite/frc-docs: Official FRC Documentation powered by Read the Docs
